---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Reply to all recipients

Usage: mxr reply-all [OPTIONS] <MESSAGE_ID>

Arguments:
  <MESSAGE_ID>  Message ID to reply to

Options:
      --body <BODY>            Inline reply body
      --body-stdin             Read body from stdin
      --signature <SIGNATURE>  Insert this signature by name instead of the scoped default
      --no-signature           Do not insert any signature
      --yes                    Skip confirmation
      --dry-run                Show what would be sent
      --format <FORMAT>        [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                   Print help
